== 軼事 ==
*此劇是[[廖麗麗|廖麗麗]]的遺作之一。
*此劇的主要演員及幕後工作人員大部分都是《[[拆局專家|拆局專家]]》原班人馬。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/160996/-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B-%E5%9B%A0-%E5%8A%87%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%AE%E9%BB%9E-%E9%BB%83%E6%99%BA%E9%9B%AF%E7%88%AD%E8%A6%96%E5%90%8E%E8%A6%81%E9%9D%A0%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2|title=【三個女人一個「因」】劇集三大亮點　黃智雯爭視后要靠呢個角色|accessdate=2018-02-07|author=|date=|publisher=}}</ref>。
*此劇是[[黄智雯|黄智雯]]繼《[[雜警奇兵|雜警奇兵]]》後再度於星期日播放的劇集，因此被封為「星期日女王」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=黃智雯不介意被封「星期日女王」：美劇都係一個禮拜一集啦|url=https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/164109/黃智雯不介意被封-星期日女王-美劇都係一個禮拜一集啦|accessdate=2019-08-15|date=2018-03-01|last=李妍樺|work=香港01|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815021142/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/164109/%E9%BB%83%E6%99%BA%E9%9B%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%8B%E6%84%8F%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81-%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%A5%B3%E7%8E%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8A%87%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E7%A6%AE%E6%8B%9C%E4%B8%80%E9%9B%86%E5%95%A6|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=“星期日女王”黄智雯杀出重围--广东频道--人民网|url=http://gd.people.com.cn/n2/2018/0315/c123932-31345377.html|accessdate=2019-08-15|work=gd.people.com.cn|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426144800/http://gd.people.com.cn/n2/2018/0315/c123932-31345377.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

